  # ABILITIES (COMICAL)
  _basicAttack:
    abilityId: naga_spit_take
    abilityName: Seven-Way Spit Take
    description: |
      All seven heads spit water at once like a broken sprinkler! 
      PTOO PTOO PTOO! "We couldn't agree on ONE direction!"
    damage: 22
    cooldown: 0
    staminaCost: 5
    range: 4.0
    type: Ranged
    element: Water

  _specialAbility:
    abilityId: naga_shed_attack
    abilityName: Shedding Season Surprise
    description: |
      The Naga Prince sheds his skin ALL AT ONCE and flings the gross, 
      slimy scales everywhere! "Sorry! It's that time of year! Ew ew ew!"
      Enemies slip on the scales and get grossed out!
    damage: 30
    cooldown: 10
    staminaCost: 35
    range: 8
    type: AoE
    element: Water
    statusEffects:
      - slip_chance_50
      - gross_out_debuff

  _ultimateAbility:
    abilityId: naga_seven_head_sneeze
    abilityName: SEVEN-HEAD SIMULTANEOUS SNEEZE
    description: |
      All seven heads sneeze at the EXACT same time! The combined snot 
      tsunami floods the entire battlefield! "AH-AH-AH-CHOOOO x7!" 
      It's disgusting AND hilarious!
    damage: 100
    cooldown: 55
    staminaCost: 80
    range: 15
    type: AoE
    element: Water
    statusEffects:
      - snot_flood_10s
      - slip_and_slide
      - everyone_grossed_out

  _passiveAbility:
    abilityId: naga_arguing_heads
    abilityName: Seven Heads, Seven Opinions
    description: |
      The seven heads argue CONSTANTLY! "Go left!" "No, RIGHT!" "UP!" 
      Enemies get so distracted watching the argument they forget to 
      attack. Sometimes allies get distracted too...
    damage: 0
    cooldown: 0
    staminaCost: 0
    range: 0
    type: Buff
    element: Water

  _comboMoves:
    - abilityId: naga_tail_tickle
      abilityName: Tail Tickle Attack
      description: |
        The Naga Prince wraps enemies and tickles them mercilessly with 
        his tail tip! "TICKLE TICKLE! SAY UNCLE!"
      damage: 40
      cooldown: 0
      staminaCost: 20
      type: Melee
      
    - abilityId: naga_hiss_fit
      abilityName: Hissy Fit
      description: |
        All seven heads throw a tantrum at once! Hissing, spitting, 
        dramatic swooning! "This is SO UNFAIR! HISSSS!"
      damage: 20
      cooldown: 12
      staminaCost: 25
      type: AoE

  # PERSONALITY
  _personality:
    bravery: 70
    kindness: 80
    wisdom: 95
    humor: 50
    loyalty: 85
    curiosity: 90

  _likes:
    - Philosophy and deep conversations
    - Surface world customs (fascinating!)
    - Pearls and shiny things
    - Rainy days
    - Spicy food (surprisingly)

  _dislikes:
    - Dry heat
    - Internal disagreements (with himself)
    - Being judged by appearance
    - Pollution
    - Having to choose one answer

  _favoriteFood: Spiced kelp rolls with pearl sauce
  _hobby: Collecting surface world objects and guessing their purpose
  _fear: That his seven heads will never truly agree, and he'll fail as a ruler
  _dream: To bridge the gap between the underwater and surface kingdoms

  # VOICE LINES (Some lines spoken by different heads!)
  _voiceLines:
    lines:
      - type: Greeting
        text: "Greetings, surface friend. We are pleased to meet you."
      - type: Greeting
        text: "The waters speak well of you." / "They do?" / "Shh!"
      - type: Selection
        text: "All seven heads agree - let us proceed!"
      - type: Selection
        text: "We are ready." / "Mostly ready." / "Five out of seven, anyway."
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "The tide turns in our favor."
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "By the depths, we shall prevail!"
      - type: Attack
        text: "Flow like water!"
      - type: Attack
        text: "Strike!" / "Now!" / "Wait, not yet!" / "Too late!"
      - type: SpecialAttack
        text: "May the rains heal your wounds!"
      - type: Ultimate
        text: "SEVEN TIDES AS ONE! RISE, GREAT WAVE!"
      - type: Hurt
        text: "We felt that!" / "All seven of us!"
      - type: LowHealth
        text: "We must... retreat to the waters..."
      - type: Victory
        text: "The tide has turned. Victory is ours."
      - type: Victory
        text: "Excellent!" / "Indeed!" / "Quite!" / "Splendid!" / "..." / "zzz..." / "Wake up!"
      - type: Defeat
        text: "The waters... will remember us..."
      - type: LevelUp
        text: "Our wisdom grows deeper, like the ocean itself."
      - type: Idle
        text: "*heads quietly argue about what to do next*"
      - type: Idle
        text: "I wonder what that cloud tastes like." / "Clouds have no taste." / "Have you tried one?"
      - type: Funny
        text: "Why did the naga go to therapy? Too many heads, too many problems!"
      - type: Funny
        text: "Being a seven-headed serpent means never losing an argument... with others."

  # RELATIONSHIPS
  _relationships:
    - characterId: champa_elephant
      characterName: Champa
      type: Friend
      affinity: 80
      relationshipDescription: |
        Champa's gentle wisdom reminds the Prince of his mother. They discuss 
        philosophy together, and she helps him mediate his internal debates.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Princess Champa sees us as one. That means more than she knows."
        - "Her wisdom rivals that of the ancient seas."

    - characterId: makara_dragon
      characterName: Makara
      type: Rival
      affinity: 45
      relationshipDescription: |
        A complex relationship. Both are water royalty, leading to competition. 
        But deep down, they respect each other's power. Classic rivals.
      specialDialogue:
        - "The dragon thinks fire makes him special. Water always wins."
        - "...We acknowledge his strength. Grudgingly."

    - characterId: kavi_monkey
      characterName: Kavi
      type: Friend
      affinity: 65
      relationshipDescription: |
        Kavi's chaos initially baffled the Prince. But over time, he learned 
        that disagreement can be... creative. Kavi taught him not to take 
        himself so seriously.
      specialDialogue:
        - "The monkey is... exhausting." / "But fun!" / "Shh!"
        - "His chaos has a strange wisdom to it."

  # BACKSTORY
  _birthplace: Crystal Palace, Underwater Naga Kingdom
  _occupation: Crown Prince / Guardian of Water
  _familyBackground: |
    Son of the Naga King (seven-headed) and Naga Queen (five-headed).
    Has several siblings, but as the seven-headed heir, he is crown prince.
  _backstory: |
    See full biography above.
  _keyMemories:
    - "Father sending me to the surface, and feeling terrified but excited."
    - "The first time all seven heads laughed at the same joke (Kavi's)."
    - "Seeing the Shadow Serpent and recognizing what division leads to."
    - "When Champa said 'You're not seven beings - you're one being with seven perspectives.'"

